com.github.mkolisnyk.cucumber.reporting.types.beans

Class CommonDataBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.mkolisnyk.cucumber.reporting.types.beans.CommonDataBean
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BenchmarkDataBean, BreakdownDataBean, ConsolidatedDataBean, CoverageDataBean, CustomReportDataBean, DetailedReportingDataBean, FeatureMapDataBean, FeatureOverviewDataBean, KnownErrorsDataBean, OverviewChartDataBean, OverviewDataBean, RetrospectiveDataBean, SystemInfoDataBean, UsageDataBean

    public class CommonDataBean
extends Object
    Represents common part of all data beans provided for reports generation. All other data beans used for each specific report generation are inherited from this class.
    Author:
    Mykola Kolisnyk

    • Field Detail

      • title

        private String title
        Contains the report title.

      • pdfPageSize

        private String pdfPageSize
        Populates the field responsible for PDF page size. The value is similar as pdfPageSize PDF export additional generation options. Values can be defined based on CSS3 Specification.

      • refreshData

        private String refreshData
        Some of the reports may contain redirect to some other file after the timeout. This string contains HTML code which performs this redirect.
